data.description: Come fall in love with this lovely home with custom touches throughout. Enjoy evenings on the spacious front porch with plenty of room for multiple seating areas. Inside, gorgeous hardwood floors stretch throughout the front flex space that would make a great formal living or dining room. Bright and open living room has a fireplace and soaring ceilings with easy access to the open concept kitchen with a breakfast bar and breakfast room with lots of natural light! Retreat to the spacious primary bedroom with an en-suite bath with vanity seating and deep soaking tub. Two more large bedrooms and full bath ensure room for everyone! The unfinished basement has loads of potential and lots of room for a man cave, playroom, home office, media room, you name it! A finished bath is already there to jump start your project. Enjoy all the privacy of a wooded backyard with no neighbors, an upper deck for entertaining, a lower covered patio for more room, and multiple level full sun garden beds!
